data.description: Fantastic home with fresh updates throughout! The floorplan has been changed to open up the flow between the dining and living areas, great for entertaining. Granite countertops, stone backsplash, gas cooktop and double oven will make meal preparation a joy. The living room features a brick fireplace and beautiful LVP flooring. The backyard with mature trees and covered patio area has plenty of room to entertain, play or just relax. Located in the highly desirable Meadow view Farms neighborhood, with easy access to shopping and major thoroughfares. This home is ready and waiting for you. Welcome home!
